{% block content %}

<section class="about__intro">
    <div class="about__intro-content" style="padding-left: 10%">
        <h6>Our History / About</h6>
        <p>Since our inception in 1987, we have had 3 expansions. Currently with over 50,000 sq. ft, our facility enables us to build injection molds that range from 50T-2500T.</p>
        <p>Our company is built on three principles: Teamwork, Hard-Work, and Integrity. These three core principles have taken us from humble beginnings to a world class supplier that Global Vehicle Brands and Leading Tier 1's can trust and rely on. </p>
        <p>Circle 5 Tool & Mold LP extends beyond our 4 walls here in Lakeshore, Canada. We have a team in Asia, as well as an extensive network of shops globally that align with our principles.</p>
        <p>With our in-house capabilities and global network, we are your partner for your global tooling needs. </p>
        <div class="about__seal">
            <p>In addition, Circle 5 Tool & Mold LP is recognized as a minority supplier under the Canadian Aboriginal and Minority Supplier Council</p>
            <img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1509460305/circle5/about__seal.png" alt="Certified Supplier CAMSC" draggable="false">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about__intro-image"><img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/darkroast-digital/image/upload/v1509460305/circle5/about__intro-image.jpg" draggable="false"></div>
</section>

<!-- End about Intro -->

<section class="about__principles">
